00:13:44,980 --> 00:13:51,060
(She stops by the Photo Room.)

263
00:14:01,470 --> 00:14:05,699
(One photo catches Eun Byul's attention.)

264
00:14:05,700 --> 00:14:09,370
(Saving you in my heart!)

265
00:14:12,410 --> 00:14:13,479
- What?
- She's looking at the photo.

266
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,480
- She's looking at it.
- The photo.

267
00:14:14,481 --> 00:14:16,310
- Don't tell me...
- For real?

268
00:14:16,910 --> 00:14:18,880
She must be looking at the photo.

269
00:14:19,350 --> 00:14:20,619
- Eun Byul must feel down...
- She saw it.

270
00:14:20,620 --> 00:14:23,189
- after the Truth Game.
- Right?

271
00:14:23,190 --> 00:14:25,120
Looking at the photo will...

272
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:27,790
- That might completely change...
- Exactly.

273
00:14:27,990 --> 00:14:29,990
Eun Byul's decision tomorrow.

274
00:14:34,430 --> 00:14:37,500
I couldn't help but feel a little disappointed.

275
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:40,000
I believe...

276
00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:43,240
I expressed my feelings quite a lot,

277
00:14:44,010 --> 00:14:47,980
but it seems that Jae Hyuk can't make up his mind.

278
00:14:49,510 --> 00:14:52,580
(Staring)

279
00:14:54,790 --> 00:14:56,550
Even so,

280
00:14:57,190 --> 00:14:58,660
I still want...

281
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:03,530
Jae Hyuk and I to get to know each other more.

282
00:15:06,060 --> 00:15:08,930
Do you have a minute to talk?

283
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:13,769
(Eun Byul asked Jae Hyuk for a chat.)

284
00:15:13,770 --> 00:15:15,110
She asked him for a chat.

285
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:19,240
She's impressive.

286
00:15:19,241 --> 00:15:21,280
- Eun Byul has changed!
- Until the last moment...

287
00:15:21,550 --> 00:15:23,180
She's being very straightforward.

288
00:15:24,620 --> 00:15:26,249
- Keep it up, Eun Byul.
- Yes.

289
00:15:26,250 --> 00:15:27,820
- Gosh.
- She's changed.

290
00:15:28,020 --> 00:15:29,020
Good luck.

291
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:33,360
I can't see anything.

292
00:15:33,660 --> 00:15:34,730
Gosh.

293
00:15:34,830 --> 00:15:36,230
Do you want to grab one?

294
00:15:36,830 --> 00:15:38,430
- We'll both carry one.
- Let's do that.

295
00:15:38,660 --> 00:15:40,800
- I feel like Harry Potter.
- Right.

296
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:43,400
- Let's go.
- Okay.

297
00:15:44,100 --> 00:15:45,370
- Are you okay?
- Yes.

298
00:15:48,170 --> 00:15:50,110
- Can you see?
- Yes, I can see well.

299
00:15:52,180 --> 00:15:57,310
(They watch the stars together on the last night.)

300
00:15:59,520 --> 00:16:00,550
You...

301
00:16:00,920 --> 00:16:03,050
What now? What is it?

302
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:05,260
Stop confusing me.

303
00:16:08,930 --> 00:16:10,560
- Why do you do that?
- What do you mean?

304
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:12,700
You know what I mean.

305
00:16:14,630 --> 00:16:16,900
- Why won't you answer me?
- What do you mean?

306
00:16:17,430 --> 00:16:18,470
Why do you do that?

307
00:16:18,770 --> 00:16:20,070
- Why do I do this?
- Yes.

308
00:16:20,470 --> 00:16:22,740
I'm not sure why.

309
00:16:24,640 --> 00:16:25,940
I asked him out...

310
00:16:26,110 --> 00:16:29,750
to see the stars together in private.

311
00:16:30,250 --> 00:16:33,350
We talked about my letter for him.

312
00:16:34,550 --> 00:16:37,250
I told him to go up to the Letter Room.

313
00:16:38,020 --> 00:16:42,090
I was hoping for confirmation.

314
00:16:43,790 --> 00:16:47,560
But I wasn't so sure about how he felt about me,

315
00:16:48,070 --> 00:16:52,000
so I was worried and anxious.

316
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:54,610
That's why I talked to him.

317
00:16:56,040 --> 00:16:58,009
- That's admirable.
- In this confusion?

318
00:16:58,010 --> 00:16:59,409
(My daughter is admirable.)

319
00:16:59,410 --> 00:17:00,609
- Here's what I think.
- Yes.

320
00:17:00,610 --> 00:17:02,509
The competition between Eun Byul and Seo Yoon...

321
00:17:02,510 --> 00:17:03,849
- has been so cute, right?
- Yes.

322
00:17:03,850 --> 00:17:07,249
I never thought that Eun Byul was competitive...

323
00:17:07,250 --> 00:17:08,589
- in relationships.
- But she is.

324
00:17:08,590 --> 00:17:10,650
- Now, I realize that she is.
- She's competitive.

325
00:17:10,950 --> 00:17:12,660
It feels a bit like cheating.

326
00:17:12,890 --> 00:17:15,159
- She asked him out at night.
- It's like she stepped on the line.

327
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:16,989
- It should be the opponent's turn, - But...

328
00:17:16,990 --> 00:17:19,059
but she pulled her foot out, saying she didn't step on it.

329
00:17:19,060 --> 00:17:20,800
But Seo Yoon secretly took a photo.

330
00:17:20,960 --> 00:17:23,170
That was in a legal setting.

331
00:17:23,270 --> 00:17:24,699
Are you saying that's an illegal setting?

332
00:17:24,700 --> 00:17:25,969
- Is that illegal?
- You can't do it in the dark.

333
00:17:25,970 --> 00:17:26,970
- What about...
- Is that illegal?

334
00:17:26,971 --> 00:17:28,510
It's cheating if you do it in the dark.

335
00:17:33,040 --> 00:17:36,709
(Jae Hyuk came upstairs to the Letter Room...)

336
00:17:36,710 --> 00:17:38,880
(after Eun Byul told him.)

337
00:17:43,590 --> 00:17:49,630
(He opens the mailbox.)

338
00:17:50,730 --> 00:17:55,030
(How will he react?)

339
00:17:57,696 --> 00:18:01,435
(Jae Hyuk came upstairs to the Letter Room...)

340
00:18:01,436 --> 00:18:03,566
(after Eun Byul told him.)

341
00:18:07,376 --> 00:18:14,246
(He opens the mailbox.)

342
00:18:15,986 --> 00:18:21,456
(Eun Byul's letter finally got to him.)

343
00:18:23,226 --> 00:18:24,226
I'm nervous.

344
00:18:24,227 --> 00:18:26,755
- It's his very first letter.
- It is.

345
00:18:26,756 --> 00:18:28,466
(He opens a letter for the very first time.)

346
00:18:34,866 --> 00:18:38,635
(To Jae Hyuk.)

347
00:18:38,636 --> 00:18:43,575
(Here's a letter that you've been dying for.)

348
00:18:43,576 --> 00:18:48,785
(I've made so many unforgettable memories here,)

349
00:18:48,786 --> 00:18:50,445
(thanks to you.)

350
00:18:50,446 --> 00:18:54,855
(I should have thanked you sooner,)

351
00:18:54,856 --> 00:18:58,026
(but I'll still thank you.)

352
00:18:58,926 --> 00:19:01,926
(They couldn't have been more awkward on the first day.)

353
00:19:02,826 --> 00:19:04,165
(Eun Byul was timid,)

354
00:19:04,166 --> 00:19:07,466
(and no one chose her in the Attraction Selection.)

355
00:19:07,696 --> 00:19:09,635
Do you want to go on a date with me today?

356
00:19:09,636 --> 00:19:15,076
(Jae Hyuk asked her out on a date the next day.)

357
00:19:16,876 --> 00:19:21,316
(She went on the date without any high hopes,)

358
00:19:21,846 --> 00:19:24,446
(but she had a good time with him.)

359
00:19:26,116 --> 00:19:30,655
(And the two expressed their feelings for each other...)

360
00:19:30,656 --> 00:19:33,656
(for the first time that day.)

361
00:19:36,326 --> 00:19:40,796
(When Jae Hyuk faltered after that,)

362
00:19:42,636 --> 00:19:46,935
(Eun Byul has consistently shown her interest in him.)

363
00:19:46,936 --> 00:19:50,376
(Eun Byul has consistently shown her interest in him.)

364
00:19:53,276 --> 00:19:54,645
(Let's make...)

365
00:19:54,646 --> 00:19:57,185
(the most out of our little time left!)

366
00:19:57,186 --> 00:20:00,055
(Great work today.)

367
00:20:00,056 --> 00:20:03,426
(I hope you zone out by the fire and have a good night.)

368
00:20:12,436 --> 00:20:14,166
He's faltering.

369
00:20:15,736 --> 00:20:18,005
His feelings for Seo Yoon are wavering again.

370
00:20:18,006 --> 00:20:19,976
I think he's faltering.

371
00:20:20,136 --> 00:20:22,945
How complicated do your feelings have to be?

372
00:20:22,946 --> 00:20:24,245
- There's so little time left.
- Right?

373
00:20:24,246 --> 00:20:26,145
- We're nearing the end.
- You don't have much time.

374
00:20:26,146 --> 00:20:27,446
You're going home soon.

375
00:20:27,816 --> 00:20:29,786
- I'm sure it's complicated.
- It is.

376
00:20:35,356 --> 00:20:37,626
(Stopping)

377
00:20:44,996 --> 00:20:49,265
(He reads Eun Byul's letter again.)

378
00:20:49,266 --> 00:20:52,076
- He's reading it again.
- He is.

379
00:20:52,476 --> 00:20:53,976
He goes over the words again.

380
00:20:56,276 --> 00:21:03,216
(He stood there and read it for a long time.)

381
00:21:06,956 --> 00:21:09,786
(Meanwhile, Hoo and Yu Bin are having a conversation.)

382
00:21:18,096 --> 00:21:20,196
(Yu Bin seems concerned for some reason.)

383
00:21:20,666 --> 00:21:21,966
Is there anything you want to say?

384
00:21:22,266 --> 00:21:24,136
- Can I be honest with you?
- Sure.

385
00:21:26,306 --> 00:21:29,145
Are you seriously considering a long-distance relationship?

386
00:21:29,146 --> 00:21:31,816
(Are you seriously considering a long-distance relationship?)

387
00:21:32,246 --> 00:21:33,246
What about you?

388
00:21:34,176 --> 00:21:35,386
Would you like me to answer first?

389
00:21:36,746 --> 00:21:38,086
Be honest.

390
00:21:39,856 --> 00:21:42,256
It hasn't been that long since we met, right?

391
00:21:42,626 --> 00:21:44,385
I'm worried that we'll grow apart...

392
00:21:44,386 --> 00:21:47,525
if we stay separated in this situation.

393
00:21:47,526 --> 00:21:51,126
Also, you'll be in college when you're there,

394
00:21:52,136 --> 00:21:56,306
so I don't even know if I'll be able to reach you...

395
00:21:57,066 --> 00:21:58,275
that often.

396
00:21:58,276 --> 00:21:59,506
That's why I wanted to know.

397
00:22:00,976 --> 00:22:02,605
Yu Bin said it from the bottom of her heart.

398
00:22:02,606 --> 00:22:03,646
Yes.

399
00:22:04,546 --> 00:22:06,515
It hasn't even been a week since we met,

400
00:22:06,516 --> 00:22:08,416
so when Hoo went back to the US,

401
00:22:08,646 --> 00:22:10,185
I wasn't sure if we could maintain our relationship...

402
00:22:10,186 --> 00:22:12,955
when we wouldn't be able to meet for months.

403
00:22:12,956 --> 00:22:15,556
So, we had a serious chat about that.

404
00:22:16,456 --> 00:22:19,756
I wish to continue my relationship with Yu Bin,

405
00:22:20,296 --> 00:22:23,026
but I must go to the US.

406
00:22:23,226 --> 00:22:25,866
I thought that might have led her to change her mind.

407
00:22:26,636 --> 00:22:30,306
That made me a bit concerned.

408
00:22:31,876 --> 00:22:34,536
Yes, they'll have to be apart for six months as soon as they meet.

409
00:22:35,006 --> 00:22:36,475
They must be worried about the long distance.

410
00:22:36,476 --> 00:22:37,675
- Yes.
- Naturally.

411
00:22:37,676 --> 00:22:38,975
- They won't be able to meet.
- Exactly.

412
00:22:38,976 --> 00:22:40,445
Hoo and Yu Bin have been doing a great job...

413
00:22:40,446 --> 00:22:41,886
of resolving misunderstandings...

414
00:22:42,216 --> 00:22:43,845
and overcoming crises,

415
00:22:43,846 --> 00:22:46,616
so we were starting to think they were an official couple.

416
00:22:47,686 --> 00:22:49,155
But the reality of a long-distance relationship...

417
00:22:49,156 --> 00:22:51,086
must be giving them second thoughts.

418
00:22:51,496 --> 00:22:53,725
If they believe they can survive a long-distance relationship,

419
00:22:53,726 --> 00:22:55,526
they'll choose each other...

420
00:22:55,726 --> 00:22:57,396
in the Final Selection tomorrow.

421
00:22:57,466 --> 00:22:59,996
- It's a new variable.
- Yes.

422
00:23:00,736 --> 00:23:06,536
(After a night filled with lingering worries,)

423
00:23:08,946 --> 00:23:14,116
(the day of the Final Selection has dawned.)

424
00:23:15,186 --> 00:23:18,786
(Woo Seo Yoon and Choi Yu Bin's room)

425
00:23:19,816 --> 00:23:22,156
Yu Bin, it's our last day together.

426
00:23:22,226 --> 00:23:23,856
Oh, no!

427
00:23:24,026 --> 00:23:25,756
No more nights for us.

428
00:23:27,856 --> 00:23:30,226
- I'm going to miss this.
- Right?

429
00:23:31,296 --> 00:23:33,236
Did you expect...

430
00:23:33,366 --> 00:23:37,635
that you'd grow feelings for someone in such a short period?

431
00:23:37,636 --> 00:23:39,576
- Never.
- Right?

432
00:23:39,636 --> 00:23:41,176
I had no idea.

433
00:23:41,746 --> 00:23:43,076
- It makes you feel that way.
- Right.

434
00:23:43,206 --> 00:23:44,945
- I didn't know it could, - Right.

435
00:23:44,946 --> 00:23:46,016
but it did.

436
00:23:48,646 --> 00:23:51,615
Maybe it's too late to say this,

437
00:23:51,616 --> 00:23:52,616
Yes?

438
00:23:52,617 --> 00:23:56,755
but when we talked about sustaining our relationship,

439
00:23:56,756 --> 00:23:58,396
even when he was in the US,

440
00:23:58,896 --> 00:24:02,166
it helped me go over my feelings once again.

441
00:24:03,326 --> 00:24:06,295
About how deep your feelings for him are?

442
00:24:06,296 --> 00:24:07,296
Yes.

443
00:24:08,406 --> 00:24:10,206
But I couldn't exactly...

444
00:24:11,036 --> 00:24:13,276
make up my mind.

445
00:24:13,476 --> 00:24:14,536
I see.

446
00:24:15,506 --> 00:24:17,246
- I think it's natural.
- Yes.

447
00:24:18,106 --> 00:24:20,375
It's a tough decision to make.

448
00:24:20,376 --> 00:24:21,376
Indeed.

449
00:24:22,286 --> 00:24:23,646
I can totally relate.

450
00:24:25,316 --> 00:24:26,816
There must be so much on your mind.

451
00:24:27,286 --> 00:24:28,526
It looks like you also have a lot on your mind.

452
00:24:28,926 --> 00:24:30,386
You're right. It's...

453
00:24:31,286 --> 00:24:33,456
I keep thinking, "I should have done it this way or that way."

454
00:24:34,356 --> 00:24:36,296
- I'm usually...
- Me too.

455
00:24:36,966 --> 00:24:38,466
- I'm usually thoughtless...
- Me too.

456
00:24:38,696 --> 00:24:40,966
- and have zero worries.
- Same.

457
00:24:41,536 --> 00:24:42,766
This place is so strange.

458
00:24:43,806 --> 00:24:44,836
It's so odd.

459
00:24:47,436 --> 00:24:50,845
I've been pretty timid,

460
00:24:50,846 --> 00:24:53,946
so I had a lot on my mind.

461
00:24:54,646 --> 00:24:56,346
But I was worried...

462
00:24:56,746 --> 00:24:59,816
that I'd only be thinking on the last day,

463
00:25:00,356 --> 00:25:04,226
so I wanted to express my feelings as long as the other person...

464
00:25:04,996 --> 00:25:06,256
didn't feel burdened.

465
00:25:10,566 --> 00:25:15,405
(Seo Yoon picked up a pen and paper.)

466
00:25:15,406 --> 00:25:17,866
(Seo Yoon picked up a pen and paper.)

467
00:25:19,276 --> 00:25:21,336
- Is she writing a letter?
- She must be.

468
00:25:23,576 --> 00:25:28,275
(She writes a letter for Jae Hyuk on the last day.)

469
00:25:28,276 --> 00:25:30,746
My last relationship ended...

470
00:25:30,846 --> 00:25:33,515
about nine months ago.

471
00:25:33,516 --> 00:25:34,586
Ever since then,

472
00:25:35,026 --> 00:25:37,186
I had never been excited about anyone...

473
00:25:37,286 --> 00:25:40,096
or grown feelings for anyone.

474
00:25:40,596 --> 00:25:43,865
My last relationship was long-distance,

475
00:25:43,866 --> 00:25:48,335
so it had been a long time since my heart fluttered.

476
00:25:48,336 --> 00:25:50,436
So it was the first time in so long.

477
00:25:53,776 --> 00:25:58,575
(She joined late and felt unfamiliar.)

478
00:25:58,576 --> 00:25:59,916
I like to be playful.

479
00:26:00,846 --> 00:26:06,186
(And Jae Hyuk approached her and made her feel comfortable.)

480
00:26:06,886 --> 00:26:10,726
(During the date, they realized...)

481
00:26:11,226 --> 00:26:14,426
(that they had numerous things in common.)

482
00:26:15,766 --> 00:26:18,496
(Woo Jae Hyuk? That's not allowed, is it?)

483
00:26:19,166 --> 00:26:21,936
(Her feelings for him grew deeper as time passed.)

484
00:26:22,136 --> 00:26:26,605
(My heart wouldn't have fluttered...)

485
00:26:26,606 --> 00:26:28,976
(if I had thought of him only as a friend.)

486
00:26:29,746 --> 00:26:30,806
I'm scared!

487
00:26:32,346 --> 00:26:36,546
(Her feelings for Jae Hyuk grew stronger.)

488
00:26:36,916 --> 00:26:38,046
I like it.

489
00:26:39,056 --> 00:26:40,555
- It's a bet.
- It's a bet!

490
00:26:40,556 --> 00:26:46,126
(And she never failed to express it with her cheerfulness.)

491
00:26:59,576 --> 00:27:04,306
(Her first and last handwritten letter for Jae Hyuk)

492
00:27:08,116 --> 00:27:10,246
However it turns out,

493
00:27:10,416 --> 00:27:13,885
I showed enough courage...

494
00:27:13,886 --> 00:27:16,556
from my end.

495
00:27:17,056 --> 00:27:19,956
So, it felt gratifying. I just felt good.

496
00:27:20,956 --> 00:27:22,995
- It is gratifying.
- She showed courage.

497
00:27:22,996 --> 00:27:24,226
- Yes.
- From her point of view.

498
00:27:24,326 --> 00:27:26,295
- That's true.
- Her feelings are sincere.

499
00:27:26,296 --> 00:27:27,366
(She showed him her sincerity.)

500
00:27:28,166 --> 00:27:31,876
(Jae Hyuk came to Hee Dong's room to hang out.)

501
00:27:32,176 --> 00:27:34,076
Shouldn't you check the mailbox before you go?

502
00:27:34,206 --> 00:27:35,406
I don't think there will be a letter.

503
00:27:37,506 --> 00:27:38,546
She might have written one.

504
00:27:41,076 --> 00:27:42,086
You think so?

505
00:27:42,446 --> 00:27:43,515
Just in case.

506
00:27:43,516 --> 00:27:46,555
(He goes to the Letter Room just in case.)

507
00:27:46,556 --> 00:27:47,616
And then...

508
00:27:48,186 --> 00:27:49,726
- You didn't?
- No.

509
00:27:54,926 --> 00:27:55,926
Thanks.

510
00:28:00,666 --> 00:28:02,135
(Hee Dong's mailbox is empty.)

511
00:28:02,136 --> 00:28:03,706
- I got nothing.
- Let me just open mine.

512
00:28:04,236 --> 00:28:05,375
We'll see.

513
00:28:05,376 --> 00:28:07,006
(Surprised)

514
00:28:09,176 --> 00:28:10,176
(He found the letter a bit late.)

515
00:28:10,177 --> 00:28:11,816
- There's a letter!
- He saw it.

516
00:28:16,486 --> 00:28:18,346
(Reading his face)

517
00:28:26,056 --> 00:28:29,496
He reads letters night and day.

518
00:28:33,266 --> 00:28:38,506
(After Hee Dong leaves, he slowly reads it.)

519
00:28:39,676 --> 00:28:43,475
(I wanted to thank you...)

520
00:28:43,476 --> 00:28:47,346
(during our 5-day stay here.)

521
00:28:48,616 --> 00:28:52,415
(You seemed to have a lot on your mind,)

522
00:28:52,416 --> 00:28:56,756
(but I want you to follow your heart and feel no pressure.)

523
00:29:00,956 --> 00:29:03,466
- He must be so torn.
- Totally.

524
00:29:04,326 --> 00:29:05,436
What should he do?

525
00:29:06,436 --> 00:29:08,566
But the timing is on Seo Yoon's side.

526
00:29:08,666 --> 00:29:10,505
His recent date was with her,

527
00:29:10,506 --> 00:29:13,276
and he got her letter the latest.

528
00:29:16,246 --> 00:29:20,146
(While he feels more and more complicated,)

529
00:29:21,746 --> 00:29:25,086
(it's 1 hour before the Final Selection.)

530
00:29:25,386 --> 00:29:26,386
- I said it.
- You asked me.

531
00:29:26,387 --> 00:29:27,815
That's why I went after you.

532
00:29:27,816 --> 00:29:28,826
(Meanwhile, in the kitchen)

533
00:29:29,556 --> 00:29:31,785
- I shouldn't have attacked you.
- Exactly.

534
00:29:31,786 --> 00:29:32,956
You shouldn't have.

535
00:29:33,296 --> 00:29:34,526
- Hi.
- Hi.

536
00:29:35,026 --> 00:29:36,996
Are you washing all the dishes from last night?

537
00:29:37,396 --> 00:29:39,566
Just do the ones here,

538
00:29:40,036 --> 00:29:42,105
and I'll take care of the rest.

539
00:29:42,106 --> 00:29:45,065
- Please leave the rest.
- That's fine.

540
00:29:45,066 --> 00:29:46,305
(Jae Hyuk heads to the kitchen.)

541
00:29:46,306 --> 00:29:47,306
I got it.

542
00:29:49,776 --> 00:29:50,846
Hey.

543
00:29:52,676 --> 00:29:54,176
You were here.

544
00:29:54,716 --> 00:29:55,946
(Laughing)

545
00:30:01,386 --> 00:30:04,626
(Jae Hyuk just leaves the room.)

546
00:30:06,056 --> 00:30:07,125
(Thinking)

547
00:30:07,126 --> 00:30:08,396
My hands are slippery.

548
00:30:11,166 --> 00:30:17,636
(To be continued in 60 seconds)

549
00:30:18,736 --> 00:30:19,776
Jae Hyuk.

550
00:30:21,406 --> 00:30:23,246
Gosh, Seo Yoon.

551
00:30:23,446 --> 00:30:25,446
- The last...
- That will make him fall for her.

552
00:30:29,846 --> 00:30:30,916
Jae Hyuk.

553
00:30:32,086 --> 00:30:33,916
Can we talk later?

554
00:30:34,446 --> 00:30:36,186
- Okay.
- In the tent.

555
00:30:36,916 --> 00:30:38,516
Let me take my coat off.

556
00:30:41,956 --> 00:30:43,796
Gosh, Seo Yoon.

557
00:30:44,026 --> 00:30:45,966
- The last...
- That will make him fall for her.

558
00:30:46,666 --> 00:30:48,065
I think she's going for the win.

559
00:30:48,066 --> 00:30:50,895
Isn't it cheating to ask for a chat at the last minute?

560
00:30:50,896 --> 00:30:52,105
- Isn't that considered cheating?
- It's not cheating.

561
00:30:52,106 --> 00:30:54,465
No, she has to do whatever it takes right now.

562
00:30:54,466 --> 00:30:57,376
(Seo Yoon has to do whatever it takes.)

563
00:30:58,536 --> 00:31:01,606
(Eun Byul is left alone in the kitchen.)

564
00:31:01,906 --> 00:31:02,916
Would she have heard them?

565
00:31:03,246 --> 00:31:06,316
She could have. Seo Yoon went, "Jae Hyuk."

566
00:31:09,356 --> 00:31:10,486
Where should we go?

567
00:31:11,056 --> 00:31:12,985
Here? Wasn't this where you wanted to go?

568
00:31:12,986 --> 00:31:14,026
It was.

569
00:31:15,556 --> 00:31:16,856
I've never gone inside it.

570
00:31:17,256 --> 00:31:18,326
Really?

571
00:31:29,936 --> 00:31:31,406
Why am I feeling nervous?

572
00:31:31,506 --> 00:31:33,706
- It's making me nervous.
- I know. So am I.

573
00:31:34,406 --> 00:31:35,815
It's her one last shot.

574
00:31:35,816 --> 00:31:37,316
(Seo Yoon's dad is also nervous.)

575
00:31:38,676 --> 00:31:40,116
It's finally...

576
00:31:41,246 --> 00:31:42,286
the end.

577
00:31:42,856 --> 00:31:44,056
- I know, right?
- Yes.

578
00:31:44,956 --> 00:31:46,326
At least I got to come to the tent.

579
00:31:56,896 --> 00:31:58,036
- But...
- Yes?

580
00:32:01,466 --> 00:32:02,536
What is it?

581
00:32:02,636 --> 00:32:06,546
Was there a moment when you weren't sure how I felt about you?

582
00:32:13,986 --> 00:32:16,586
- No?
- No. I never...

583
00:32:17,016 --> 00:32:18,616
felt that you were...

584
00:32:19,756 --> 00:32:22,156
showing your interest in anyone else.

585
00:32:24,056 --> 00:32:25,526
So, I could tell...

586
00:32:26,596 --> 00:32:28,526
that you were expressing your feelings for me.

587
00:32:30,036 --> 00:32:31,136
- That's true.
- Yes.

588
00:32:31,236 --> 00:32:32,366
- You're right.
- Yes.

589
00:32:33,966 --> 00:32:35,366
You're right, but...

590
00:32:36,476 --> 00:32:37,906
It's just that...

591
00:32:38,476 --> 00:32:41,206
I felt like I only said it was fun.

592
00:32:41,546 --> 00:32:42,576
I was a bit...

593
00:32:43,616 --> 00:32:45,446
I was just...

594
00:32:45,546 --> 00:32:49,886
worried that you might think I was only having fun.

595
00:32:58,826 --> 00:32:59,826
There you go.

596
00:32:59,996 --> 00:33:01,096
Well done.

597
00:33:01,266 --> 00:33:04,266
"I didn't have feelings for you just for fun."

598
00:33:04,796 --> 00:33:06,506
Until the end,

599
00:33:06,536 --> 00:33:08,975
she tells him how she feels exactly and honestly.

600
00:33:08,976 --> 00:33:10,336
(She tells him how she thinks exactly until the end.)

601
00:33:11,206 --> 00:33:14,976
Even if someone does something boring, it'll look fun...

602
00:33:15,446 --> 00:33:17,176
- if you like that person.
- Right.

603
00:33:17,416 --> 00:33:19,146
That's exactly what I think.

604
00:33:19,946 --> 00:33:22,756
Even just going to a cafe...

605
00:33:22,856 --> 00:33:24,416
or doing nothing...

606
00:33:25,556 --> 00:33:26,886
- is fun.
- Just by being together.

607
00:33:27,356 --> 00:33:28,996
Being together is what makes it fun.

608
00:33:29,256 --> 00:33:30,756
Not because you do something.

609
00:33:34,166 --> 00:33:38,066
I just wanted to tell you in case you misunderstood.

610
00:33:38,436 --> 00:33:39,566
That's not the case.

611
00:33:40,436 --> 00:33:43,176
No, I never thought like that.

612
00:33:45,006 --> 00:33:46,076
I see.

613
00:33:46,846 --> 00:33:47,876
I'm relieved, then.

614
00:33:49,576 --> 00:33:52,316
- She told him that she's serious.
- That's so nice.

615
00:33:54,486 --> 00:33:57,056
Jae Hyuk must have a lot on his mind too.

616
00:33:59,726 --> 00:34:02,726
He wouldn't have felt all that comfortable.

617
00:34:02,926 --> 00:34:04,826
Still, before the Final Selection,

618
00:34:04,996 --> 00:34:06,426
I wanted to express myself all the way.

619
00:34:14,906 --> 00:34:19,446
Both of them showed that they were serious about me.

620
00:34:20,446 --> 00:34:22,176
Why do you make me feel so confused?

621
00:34:22,746 --> 00:34:25,416
They're showing so much interest in someone like me.

622
00:34:26,986 --> 00:34:28,586
I'm very grateful for it, really.

623
00:34:29,156 --> 00:34:30,156
But...

624
00:34:31,086 --> 00:34:33,626
I must choose one of them.

625
00:34:34,286 --> 00:34:38,656
I felt bad for the other person,

626
00:34:39,566 --> 00:34:40,566
and it weighed heavily on my mind.

627
00:34:43,036 --> 00:34:48,766
(The person Jae Hyuk feels bad for)

628
00:34:49,276 --> 00:34:52,075
(Is it Seo Yoon...)

629
00:34:52,076 --> 00:34:55,946
(or Eun Byul?)

630
00:34:57,846 --> 00:35:00,786
They're both so charming.

631
00:35:01,086 --> 00:35:04,315
In that situation, whether Jae Hyuk chooses Eun Byul or Seo Yoon,

632
00:35:04,316 --> 00:35:06,455
one of them will get hurt.

633
00:35:06,456 --> 00:35:09,525
- Exactly.
- So he feels bad.

634
00:35:09,526 --> 00:35:11,925
- He might end up not choosing.
- Yes. He'll feel overwhelmed.

635
00:35:11,926 --> 00:35:14,226
That's the day of the Selection.

636
00:35:22,166 --> 00:35:25,906
(It's time for the Final Selection.)

637
00:35:26,476 --> 00:35:31,016
(Write your final letter to the person you have feelings for.)

638
00:35:31,716 --> 00:35:34,385
(Don't put the final letter into the mailbox.)

639
00:35:34,386 --> 00:35:36,786
(Instead, give it to the recipient yourself.)

640
00:35:37,286 --> 00:35:39,285
(If there's nobody you have feelings for,)

641
00:35:39,286 --> 00:35:41,326
(you may leave without writing a letter.)

642
00:35:41,556 --> 00:35:43,996
- It's time for the Final Selection.
- It's time for the Final Selection.

643
00:35:44,826 --> 00:35:47,726
Finally, it's time for the Final Selection.

644
00:35:48,196 --> 00:35:51,865
"Write your final letter to the person you have feelings for."

645
00:35:51,866 --> 00:35:54,536
(They make their Final Selection by handing over the final letter.)

646
00:35:56,306 --> 00:35:58,275
It's time to make up their minds.

647
00:35:58,276 --> 00:36:01,246
(It's really time to make up their minds.)

648
00:36:02,416 --> 00:36:06,446
(Si Woo is the first person to come to the Letter Room.)

649
00:36:16,356 --> 00:36:17,426
Well...

650
00:36:18,456 --> 00:36:19,566
I...

651
00:36:20,426 --> 00:36:23,096
My heart...

652
00:36:23,836 --> 00:36:28,066
feels fuzzy, and I get all choked up.

653
00:36:29,236 --> 00:36:31,806
Because this is really the end,

654
00:36:32,276 --> 00:36:33,575
and all the moments...

655
00:36:33,576 --> 00:36:37,145
from the first day I came here until now...

656
00:36:37,146 --> 00:36:38,576
flashed before my eyes.

657
00:36:42,716 --> 00:36:47,785
(She looks back on the past days.)

658
00:36:47,786 --> 00:36:50,356
- Si Woo went through a lot.
- Right.

659
00:36:58,136 --> 00:37:03,835
(She writes each and every letter of the final letter with sincerity.)

660
00:37:03,836 --> 00:37:07,546
(She writes each and every letter of the final letter with sincerity.)

661
00:37:08,976 --> 00:37:14,046
The person who made me feel most comfortable and fun until now.

662
00:37:14,316 --> 00:37:15,986
Who I'm grateful to as well.

663
00:37:16,716 --> 00:37:19,585
I wrote my genuine feelings,

664
00:37:19,586 --> 00:37:22,656
so even if it doesn't reach her...

665
00:37:23,626 --> 00:37:24,626
I have no regrets.

666
00:37:30,296 --> 00:37:35,066
(They made countless memories here.)

667
00:37:36,476 --> 00:37:42,106
(What kind of the Final Selection...)

668
00:37:43,716 --> 00:37:50,556
(will our kids make?)

669
00:37:50,616 --> 00:37:53,126
It's Jae Hyuk's turn.

670
00:37:55,026 --> 00:38:00,496
(Jae Hyuk sits at the desk last.)

671
00:38:05,566 --> 00:38:12,106
(He hesitates to write.)

672
00:38:22,086 --> 00:38:27,656
(After a long consideration, he starts to write the letter.)

673
00:38:30,126 --> 00:38:33,896
I thought I should express...

674
00:38:34,366 --> 00:38:36,296
my feelings clearly now.

675
00:38:42,036 --> 00:38:44,336
I had fun when I was with her,

676
00:38:44,876 --> 00:38:46,676
and I want to get to know her more.

677
00:38:47,806 --> 00:38:51,046
"You're my final choice." That's what I wrote.

678
00:39:01,856 --> 00:39:05,825
(Jae Hyuk takes the letter...)

679
00:39:05,826 --> 00:39:12,636
(which contains his feelings and leaves the room.)

680
00:39:14,706 --> 00:39:21,046
(Our kids have made up their minds.)

681
00:39:21,306 --> 00:39:23,016
The most important key point is...

682
00:39:23,916 --> 00:39:25,415
- Jae Hyuk.
- Jae Hyuk.

683
00:39:25,416 --> 00:39:26,746
Who will he choose?

684
00:39:26,986 --> 00:39:28,716
Eun Byul or Seo Yoon?

685
00:39:29,086 --> 00:39:31,516
Let's hear out the parents' gut feelings.

686
00:39:32,216 --> 00:39:34,786
I'd like to cast my vote...

687
00:39:35,156 --> 00:39:36,895
- to Seo Yoon and her final spurt.
- Seo Yoon.

688
00:39:36,896 --> 00:39:40,066
Based on the timing, Seo Yoon has the advantage.

689
00:39:40,666 --> 00:39:43,435
She wrote the letter and went on the date with him...

690
00:39:43,436 --> 00:39:44,636
after Eun Byul did.

691
00:39:45,136 --> 00:39:46,906
So Seo Yoon's afterimage remains stronger.

692
00:39:47,406 --> 00:39:49,876
That's why I think Seo Yoon has the advantage.

693
00:39:50,006 --> 00:39:51,906
Two votes for Seo Yoon. Hoo's dad?

694
00:39:52,476 --> 00:39:53,775
I think it's Eun Byul.

695
00:39:53,776 --> 00:39:55,405
- Eun Byul.
- Eun Byul.

696
00:39:55,406 --> 00:39:56,975
Jae Hyuk will still go for Eun Byul.

697
00:39:56,976 --> 00:39:58,315
If I must choose one,

698
00:39:58,316 --> 00:40:00,585
- I think it's Eun Byul.
- Really?

699
00:40:00,586 --> 00:40:03,086
He was already quite steady with her.

700
00:40:03,656 --> 00:40:05,585
- It's two-all.
- I felt it.

701
00:40:05,586 --> 00:40:07,226
- Two-all. Yu Bin's dad.
- When it's complicated...

702
00:40:07,356 --> 00:40:09,756
It's such a complicated issue. But I'll think about it simply.

703
00:40:10,156 --> 00:40:12,426
When I was young and received a love letter...

704
00:40:12,456 --> 00:40:14,825
from someone I liked, I wanted to read it again.

705
00:40:14,826 --> 00:40:16,635
- He read it twice.
- Yes, he read it twice.

706
00:40:16,636 --> 00:40:18,235
- He read Eun Byul's letter twice.
- Whose letter did he read?

707
00:40:18,236 --> 00:40:19,836
It was Eun Byul's. So he'll choose Eun Byul.

708
00:40:20,706 --> 00:40:22,606
It's 3-2.

709
00:40:22,936 --> 00:40:24,835
Eun Byul is taking a slight lead.

710
00:40:24,836 --> 00:40:26,246
- For now, yes.
- Right.

711
00:40:26,706 --> 00:40:28,446
For Yoon Hoo and Yu Bin,

712
00:40:28,646 --> 00:40:31,415
we don't know what might happen because of the long-distance issue.

713
00:40:31,416 --> 00:40:32,816
I think in this case,

714
00:40:33,146 --> 00:40:36,485
Yu Bin might just leave without making her Final Selection.

715
00:40:36,486 --> 00:40:37,555
I agree.

716
00:40:37,556 --> 00:40:40,886
As a dad with a daughter, if they work out,

717
00:40:41,056 --> 00:40:44,826
I'd like them to build a nice future.

718
00:40:45,096 --> 00:40:47,296
But if that won't happen, I think...

719
00:40:47,796 --> 00:40:50,695
it might be better to part ways now.

720
00:40:50,696 --> 00:40:51,766
Because...

721
00:40:52,196 --> 00:40:54,935
if they continue to meet each other,

722
00:40:54,936 --> 00:40:57,006
they'll keep eating and ruin their health.

723
00:40:57,676 --> 00:41:00,106
They might negatively affect...

724
00:41:01,006 --> 00:41:02,816
each other.

725
00:41:03,246 --> 00:41:04,445
I think both of them won't choose...

726
00:41:04,446 --> 00:41:05,876
and communicate via the letters instead.

727
00:41:06,046 --> 00:41:07,116
Like how?

728
00:41:07,386 --> 00:41:10,756
"If we still think about each other even when we're far away,"

729
00:41:11,016 --> 00:41:13,525
- "let's think about it seriously." - Think about it later?

730
00:41:13,526 --> 00:41:15,786
When they see a clearer future.

731
00:41:17,196 --> 00:41:20,696
(Our kids' Final Selection)

732
00:41:22,196 --> 00:41:25,765
(The daughters are waiting...)

733
00:41:25,766 --> 00:41:30,936
(at their final locations.)

734
00:41:33,146 --> 00:41:34,905
(Final Selection Rule)

735
00:41:34,906 --> 00:41:40,816
(The men will head to the location where the woman they chose is at.)

736
00:41:41,916 --> 00:41:45,285
(If they chose each other, they'll meet at the same location.)

737
00:41:45,286 --> 00:41:51,726
(If they chose each other, they'll meet at the same location.)

738
00:41:55,226 --> 00:41:58,696
(Park Si Woo at the Final Selection location)

739
00:42:02,506 --> 00:42:06,145
I only wanted Hee Dong and no one else.

740
00:42:06,146 --> 00:42:09,006
(Final Selection: Park Si Woo chose You Hee Dong.)

741
00:42:10,016 --> 00:42:13,645
(Is Hee Dong heading to...)

742
00:42:13,646 --> 00:42:19,116
(where Si Woo is?)

743
00:42:19,556 --> 00:42:23,356
There's no way Hee Dong would go to someone else, right?

744
00:42:23,996 --> 00:42:25,555
Are you still worried?

745
00:42:25,556 --> 00:42:27,226
- You're still anxious?
- But what if...

746
00:42:27,526 --> 00:42:28,965
Since this is the Final Selection.

747
00:42:28,966 --> 00:42:30,365
Gosh, Si Woo's dad is...

748
00:42:30,366 --> 00:42:33,035
- very worried.
- What if Si Woo...

749
00:42:33,036 --> 00:42:34,736
(Who did Hee Dong choose?)

750
00:42:42,946 --> 00:42:44,075
He's opening the door.

751
00:42:44,076 --> 00:42:46,446
(Anxious)

752
00:43:09,836 --> 00:43:12,736
(Final Couple: You Hee Dong and Park Si Woo)

753
00:43:13,846 --> 00:43:16,145
(The dads are also happy that they met.)

754
00:43:16,146 --> 00:43:18,576
You can easily tell from that face.

755
00:43:18,776 --> 00:43:20,816
- You can tell right away.
- Yes.

756
00:43:22,016 --> 00:43:24,015
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

757
00:43:24,016 --> 00:43:25,385
(The first couple is formed! Hee Dong and Si Woo)

758
00:43:25,386 --> 00:43:28,055
- The first couple is formed.
- Congratulations.

759
00:43:28,056 --> 00:43:30,526
As expected, Si Woo and Hee Dong didn't change.

760
00:43:30,626 --> 00:43:32,755
- That's right.
- That's our first couple.

761
00:43:32,756 --> 00:43:33,965
- Congratulations.
- Park Nam Jung and You Tae Woong,

762
00:43:33,966 --> 00:43:35,495
- congratulations.
- Congratulations.

763
00:43:35,496 --> 00:43:37,096
(The dads feel proud.)

764
00:43:37,936 --> 00:43:38,966
Did you wait long?

765
00:43:39,496 --> 00:43:40,666
- Did you wait long?
- No.

766
00:43:42,136 --> 00:43:44,876
You looked upset about the withered flowers.

767
00:43:45,276 --> 00:43:47,146
- Don't be upset.
- Thanks.

768
00:43:47,906 --> 00:43:48,946
Thank you.

769
00:43:51,446 --> 00:43:52,446
Here.

770
00:43:52,447 --> 00:43:58,116
(The bouquet she received from Hee Dong on the first day)

771
00:43:59,456 --> 00:44:02,656
(I put it by my window.)

772
00:44:02,756 --> 00:44:05,425
(In case it withers.)

773
00:44:05,426 --> 00:44:07,396
I thought it'd wither less if it got some sunlight.

774
00:44:09,026 --> 00:44:13,866
(Following the first day,)

775
00:44:15,606 --> 00:44:20,476
(Hee Dong bought a bouquet of flowers on the last day as well.)

776
00:44:21,746 --> 00:44:23,146
