you've always been the one for me since then.

1035
00:59:59,416 --> 01:00:00,516
That's nice.

1036
01:00:03,216 --> 01:00:06,816
I'll need to go back to the US.

1037
01:00:07,356 --> 01:00:10,656
I hope we'll meet before that happens.

1038
01:00:11,426 --> 01:00:14,426
Although we've had many conversations,

1039
01:00:14,526 --> 01:00:18,666
I want to go on a date with you outside the show...

1040
01:00:19,596 --> 01:00:22,436
and get to know you better.

1041
01:00:22,536 --> 01:00:26,876
It'll be nice to talk about how to proceed from here.

1042
01:00:28,506 --> 01:00:29,546
That sounds good.

1043
01:00:31,516 --> 01:00:32,516
Okay.

1044
01:00:34,086 --> 01:00:39,156
You're my Final Selection, Choi Yu Bin.

1045
01:00:39,556 --> 01:00:40,886
I'm happy to leave the show with you.

1046
01:00:41,356 --> 01:00:42,356
- Really?
- Yes.

1047
01:00:42,656 --> 01:00:43,726
To my dad,

1048
01:00:45,056 --> 01:00:46,056
I'll brag about you.

1049
01:00:48,066 --> 01:00:49,795
(Their dads are happy too.)

1050
01:00:49,796 --> 01:00:51,836
He talks like an adult.

1051
01:00:51,966 --> 01:00:53,236
He seems like a tough guy.

1052
01:00:53,636 --> 01:00:55,005
"I'm happy to leave the show with you."

1053
01:00:55,006 --> 01:00:56,006
(Impressed)

1054
01:00:56,806 --> 01:00:58,276
Yu Bin's facial expression tells me...

1055
01:00:59,006 --> 01:01:01,446
that she is incredibly happy.

1056
01:01:05,946 --> 01:01:08,586
Yu Bin made my heart flutter the most...

1057
01:01:09,216 --> 01:01:10,316
when she fell asleep...

1058
01:01:11,916 --> 01:01:13,116
in the car.

1059
01:01:14,156 --> 01:01:17,155
I was used to seeing Yu Bin...

1060
01:01:17,156 --> 01:01:20,766
take the lead and make an effort.

1061
01:01:21,426 --> 01:01:24,136
When she was sleeping, I honestly thought...

1062
01:01:24,596 --> 01:01:26,066
she looked lovely.

1063
01:01:26,966 --> 01:01:28,865
That was when...

1064
01:01:28,866 --> 01:01:32,036
she looked the cutest...

1065
01:01:32,376 --> 01:01:33,906
and made my heart flutter the most.

1066
01:01:36,146 --> 01:01:37,616
She is someone...

1067
01:01:38,016 --> 01:01:40,446
who makes me grateful that I've met her.

1068
01:01:42,346 --> 01:01:43,886
- Really?
- That's so nice.

1069
01:01:46,856 --> 01:01:47,926
My heart fluttered.

1070
01:01:48,686 --> 01:01:50,656
I felt a bit embarrassed,

1071
01:01:51,196 --> 01:01:53,896
so I purposefully avoided eye contact.

1072
01:01:54,926 --> 01:01:58,195
I didn't think that I'd become interested in someone...

1073
01:01:58,196 --> 01:02:00,236
in such a short time.

1074
01:02:00,966 --> 01:02:03,036
I'm fascinated that it has happened.

1075
01:02:10,606 --> 01:02:11,616
Make it pretty.

1076
01:02:16,586 --> 01:02:18,386
My ideal type is the Little Match Girl.

1077
01:02:19,986 --> 01:02:21,026
Stay still.

1078
01:02:22,456 --> 01:02:23,485
Okay.

1079
01:02:23,486 --> 01:02:24,726
Let me answer! An Egyptian mummy.

1080
01:02:26,026 --> 01:02:27,196
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

1081
01:02:30,166 --> 01:02:32,035
Why do you look so pretty in the photo...

1082
01:02:32,036 --> 01:02:33,036
you took with Hee Dong?

1083
01:02:33,336 --> 01:02:34,336
It's annoying.

1084
01:02:34,536 --> 01:02:36,136
Don't worry about that.

1085
01:02:36,436 --> 01:02:37,476
I'm joking.

1086
01:02:37,936 --> 01:02:39,976
They're holding hands. They're leaving hand in hand.

1087
01:02:41,046 --> 01:02:42,245
(The two of them became very close.)

1088
01:02:42,246 --> 01:02:43,476
I'm jealous.

1089
01:02:43,646 --> 01:02:45,115
- We got another couple.
- Yes.

1090
01:02:45,116 --> 01:02:46,216
(The two of them became very close.)

1091
01:02:46,346 --> 01:02:47,446
They look good together.

1092
01:02:48,216 --> 01:02:50,116
They still might be a couple as well.

1093
01:02:50,756 --> 01:02:52,385
- I know.
- I bet they are.

1094
01:02:52,386 --> 01:02:53,716
It went as we expected.

1095
01:02:53,986 --> 01:02:55,525
Do you like your son-in-law?

1096
01:02:55,526 --> 01:02:57,285
I really like him.

1097
01:02:57,286 --> 01:03:01,395
I got to watch how Hoo behaved early on...

1098
01:03:01,396 --> 01:03:04,196
and how he treated other girls.

1099
01:03:04,596 --> 01:03:06,036
From what I've seen,

1100
01:03:06,436 --> 01:03:08,866
I think he'll be a great son-in-law even if he ends up with someone...

1101
01:03:09,236 --> 01:03:10,805
other than my daughter.

1102
01:03:10,806 --> 01:03:13,835
So I'll welcome him with open arms.

1103
01:03:13,836 --> 01:03:14,846
- Okay.
- Yes.

1104
01:03:15,206 --> 01:03:18,176
Firstly, they have clear similarities.

1105
01:03:18,576 --> 01:03:20,575
- Food.
- They enjoy eating.

1106
01:03:20,576 --> 01:03:22,986
Yu Bin has a talent for cooking.

1107
01:03:23,646 --> 01:03:24,956
- That's right.
- In that sense,

1108
01:03:25,356 --> 01:03:27,385
- they make a good couple.
- Yes.

1109
01:03:27,386 --> 01:03:30,126
Min Soo and Jae Won, congratulations.

1110
01:03:30,326 --> 01:03:32,596
All of us thought they might become a couple.

1111
01:03:32,726 --> 01:03:34,565
They actually became a couple.

1112
01:03:34,566 --> 01:03:35,626
(The second couple makes the parents happy.)

1113
01:03:39,396 --> 01:03:42,006
(Woo Seo Yoon at the Final Selection location)

1114
01:03:43,436 --> 01:03:44,676
As I waited,

1115
01:03:44,876 --> 01:03:47,676
I hoped that Jae Hyuk would come.

1116
01:03:47,906 --> 01:03:51,376
(Final Selection: Woo Seo Yoon chose Shin Jae Hyuk.)

1117
01:03:51,616 --> 01:03:55,146
Seo Yoon delivered her sincerity to Jae Hyuk until the last day.

1118
01:03:56,946 --> 01:04:00,215
I made up my mind to go...

1119
01:04:00,216 --> 01:04:02,826
with my first choice...

1120
01:04:03,086 --> 01:04:05,795
and chose Jae Hyuk.

1121
01:04:05,796 --> 01:04:07,326
(Final Selection: Cho Eun Byul chose Shin Jae Hyuk.)

1122
01:04:07,766 --> 01:04:09,065
- My goodness.
- Eun Byul too.

1123
01:04:09,066 --> 01:04:11,136
- Eun Byul too.
- She chose Jae Hyuk as always.

1124
01:04:12,066 --> 01:04:15,906
(Jae Hyuk has been chosen by two people.)

1125
01:04:16,336 --> 01:04:17,676
I can't watch this.

1126
01:04:18,106 --> 01:04:19,275
This is...

1127
01:04:19,276 --> 01:04:21,445
(Jae Hyuk's choice will determine the last couple.)

1128
01:04:21,446 --> 01:04:22,846
He doesn't need to walk so hurriedly.

1129
01:04:23,646 --> 01:04:25,746
- Why am I nervous?
- It's nerve-racking.

1130
01:04:27,046 --> 01:04:30,746
I wasn't certain that Jae Hyuk would choose me,

1131
01:04:31,186 --> 01:04:34,456
so it was very nerve-racking.

1132
01:04:39,596 --> 01:04:42,426
He seemed to be torn,

1133
01:04:42,866 --> 01:04:44,896
so I was anxious.

1134
01:04:47,136 --> 01:04:49,736
(Jae Hyuk heads over to the Final Selection location.)

1135
01:04:49,936 --> 01:04:51,575
- My goodness.
- Jae Hyuk.

1136
01:04:51,576 --> 01:04:53,305
- Jae Hyuk, where are you going?
- Where are you going?

1137
01:04:53,306 --> 01:04:55,606
- Oh, no.
- One of them will cry.

1138
01:04:56,946 --> 01:04:58,146
Gosh, this is...

1139
01:04:59,516 --> 01:05:02,646
(To whom will Jae Hyuk's heart head?)

1140
01:05:04,186 --> 01:05:06,855
(Seo Yoon who expressed her interest until the end?)

1141
01:05:06,856 --> 01:05:09,586
- She is looking for him.
- Seo Yoon is waiting.

1142
01:05:10,186 --> 01:05:13,495
(Eun Byul who clicked with him from the start?)

1143
01:05:13,496 --> 01:05:14,726
Eun Byul is waiting too.

1144
01:05:16,596 --> 01:05:21,306
(To whom did Jae Hyuk go?)

1145
01:05:28,446 --> 01:05:29,706
- What?
- What?

1146
01:05:42,656 --> 01:05:46,425
(Final Couple: Shin Jae Hyuk and Cho Eun Byul)

1147
01:05:46,426 --> 01:05:50,426
(Final Couple: Shin Jae Hyuk and Cho Eun Byul)

1148
01:05:50,626 --> 01:05:51,795
- What?
- He came.

1149
01:05:51,796 --> 01:05:53,135
(Jae Hyuk chose Eun Byul for the Final Selection.)

1150
01:05:53,136 --> 01:05:55,806
- Jae Hyuk came to Eun Byul.
- He came.

1151
01:05:56,436 --> 01:05:57,465
I got it right.

1152
01:05:57,466 --> 01:05:59,236
(Congratulations.)

1153
01:05:59,436 --> 01:06:01,206
Jae Hyuk chose Eun Byul.

1154
01:06:01,906 --> 01:06:05,175
She became so startled.

1155
01:06:05,176 --> 01:06:07,145
- I became so startled.
- That's right.

1156
01:06:07,146 --> 01:06:08,445
I became so startled...

1157
01:06:08,446 --> 01:06:10,985
because I thought he'd go to Seo Yoon.

1158
01:06:10,986 --> 01:06:12,785
- Is that so?
- Since she pushed very hard...

1159
01:06:12,786 --> 01:06:14,056
at the end,

1160
01:06:14,486 --> 01:06:17,225
I thought Jae Hyuk would be captivated.

1161
01:06:17,226 --> 01:06:21,065
Seo Yoon made a move on him at the end,

1162
01:06:21,066 --> 01:06:23,796
and the two of them got along very well.

1163
01:06:23,996 --> 01:06:25,296
So I didn't know who he'd choose.

1164
01:06:25,396 --> 01:06:27,035
But I think the affection he had...

1165
01:06:27,036 --> 01:06:28,906
- at the bottom of his heart...
- Okay.

1166
01:06:28,936 --> 01:06:30,766
led him to Eun Byul at the end.

1167
01:06:31,876 --> 01:06:33,575
- I see.
- Coach Shin, we had...

1168
01:06:33,576 --> 01:06:36,005
- so many ups and downs.
- Sung Mi.

1169
01:06:36,006 --> 01:06:37,715
- All right.
- Thank you for your hard work.

1170
01:06:37,716 --> 01:06:39,845
- Tae Yong.
- They ended up together.

1171
01:06:39,846 --> 01:06:41,545
(After many struggles, the third couple was born.)

1172
01:06:41,546 --> 01:06:42,785
- Seriously.
- Jae Hyuk and Eun Byul are...

1173
01:06:42,786 --> 01:06:44,016
the third couple.

1174
01:06:45,986 --> 01:06:47,156
Hello.

1175
01:06:51,426 --> 01:06:52,496
Hello.

1176
01:07:05,136 --> 01:07:06,206
Did you wait long?

1177
01:07:07,036 --> 01:07:08,505
- Just a little bit.
- A little bit?

1178
01:07:08,506 --> 01:07:09,546
Yes.

1179
01:07:12,446 --> 01:07:13,946
- I didn't have...
- Yes?

1180
01:07:15,216 --> 01:07:16,785
expectations.

1181
01:07:16,786 --> 01:07:18,086
- Really?
- Yes.

1182
01:07:18,116 --> 01:07:19,116
Why?

1183
01:07:20,656 --> 01:07:22,786
You didn't seem to be certain.

1184
01:07:23,026 --> 01:07:25,356
You seemed to be torn.

1185
01:07:28,196 --> 01:07:29,826
So I wasn't sure...

1186
01:07:30,496 --> 01:07:32,236
what would happen in the end.

1187
01:07:40,476 --> 01:07:43,445
My choice for the Final Selection is Eun Byul.

1188
01:07:43,446 --> 01:07:45,216
(Jae Hyuk's choice for the Final Selection, Eun Byul)

1189
01:07:46,516 --> 01:07:49,946
(Jae Hyuk received Eun Byul's letter last night.)

1190
01:07:50,346 --> 01:07:51,716
Reading the letter...

1191
01:07:52,886 --> 01:07:54,856
reminded me of the good time...

1192
01:07:54,956 --> 01:07:56,926
I had with Eun Byul.

1193
01:08:03,066 --> 01:08:05,936
So I sat down and became lost in thought...

1194
01:08:06,666 --> 01:08:08,306
for a few minutes.

1195
01:08:10,466 --> 01:08:13,136
Then I wrote a letter to Eun Byul.

1196
01:08:13,536 --> 01:08:14,945
Did he write a reply?

1197
01:08:14,946 --> 01:08:16,306
- What?
- I see.

1198
01:08:17,816 --> 01:08:24,386
(Jae Hyuk's letter reached Eun Byul.)

1199
01:08:26,416 --> 01:08:31,555
(Your words that you had new experiences through me...)

1200
01:08:31,556 --> 01:08:34,056
(moved me so much.)

1201
01:08:34,426 --> 01:08:35,726
I was torn, but...

1202
01:08:36,566 --> 01:08:37,936
Until now,

1203
01:08:38,396 --> 01:08:42,136
I thought an ideal type was something like love at first sight.

1204
01:08:42,936 --> 01:08:45,236
But going on dates with Eun Byul...

1205
01:08:45,906 --> 01:08:47,106
and conversing with her...

1206
01:08:48,506 --> 01:08:50,876
helped me find my ideal type.

1207
01:08:51,816 --> 01:08:53,646
Someone who is relaxed and funny...

1208
01:08:54,046 --> 01:08:57,085
Someone I can enjoy a good time and a good conversation with...

1209
01:08:57,086 --> 01:08:59,486
is my ideal type.

1210
01:09:03,986 --> 01:09:05,556
I can breathe easy now.

1211
01:09:06,696 --> 01:09:08,195
(Eun Byul is finally relieved.)

1212
01:09:08,196 --> 01:09:10,225
- Her mom feels the same.
- Seriously.

1213
01:09:10,226 --> 01:09:11,435
You went through a lot, Eun Byul.

1214
01:09:11,436 --> 01:09:13,295
That's how a mom feels.

1215
01:09:13,296 --> 01:09:15,066
- That's right.
- Well done, Eun Byul.

1216
01:09:16,466 --> 01:09:18,476
My mind is at ease now.

1217
01:09:19,406 --> 01:09:20,676
I'm happy.

1218
01:09:29,416 --> 01:09:32,516
(Another person who was waiting for Jae Hyuk)

1219
01:09:40,656 --> 01:09:47,636
(The Final Selection has ended.)

1220
01:09:48,136 --> 01:09:49,805
- What?
- Seo Yoon.

1221
01:09:49,806 --> 01:09:50,906
He didn't come.

1222
01:09:51,306 --> 01:09:52,575
Jae Hyuk didn't come.

1223
01:09:52,576 --> 01:09:54,335
- How upsetting.
- Seo Yoon,

1224
01:09:54,336 --> 01:09:55,906
don't let it hurt your feelings.

1225
01:10:06,156 --> 01:10:10,956
(In the end, Seo Yoon's letter doesn't reach him.)

1226
01:10:21,566 --> 01:10:24,435
(To Bryan. You know that you weren't just funny, right?)

1227
01:10:24,436 --> 01:10:29,346
(You seem like a really cool and nice person.)

1228
01:10:30,876 --> 01:10:32,615
(Like I said earlier,)

1229
01:10:32,616 --> 01:10:34,315
(I hope you'll take it easy.)

1230
01:10:34,316 --> 01:10:40,086
(I hope you'll take it easy.)

1231
01:10:40,986 --> 01:10:46,596
(It's the last day, so enjoy yourself.)

1232
01:10:47,726 --> 01:10:53,366
(Thank you for everything. Good luck!)

1233
01:10:54,506 --> 01:10:55,966
Seo Yoon is so cool.

1234
01:11:12,456 --> 01:11:16,256
(How does it feel right now?)

1235
01:11:18,626 --> 01:11:20,556
I think my dad will be upset...

1236
01:11:21,526 --> 01:11:23,226
because I'm upset.

1237
01:11:30,636 --> 01:11:32,076
Why am I crying? Seriously.

1238
01:11:32,836 --> 01:11:35,346
I'm not very upset,

1239
01:11:37,006 --> 01:11:39,146
but Dad doesn't know how I feel.

1240
01:11:39,916 --> 01:11:41,046
So...

1241
01:11:42,246 --> 01:11:44,816
it makes my heart ache. I'm already worried about that.

1242
01:11:44,856 --> 01:11:46,016
I'm worried again.

1243
01:11:46,416 --> 01:11:50,126
(Seo Yoon worries about her dad first.)

1244
01:11:52,126 --> 01:11:54,056
Why is she crying? For goodness' sake.

1245
01:11:56,096 --> 01:11:57,295
It's okay.

1246
01:11:57,296 --> 01:11:59,096
- She thinks about her dad first.
- I'm okay.

1247
01:12:03,406 --> 01:12:04,436
That's right.

1248
01:12:04,466 --> 01:12:06,775
Seo Yoon thinks about her dad first.

1249
01:12:06,776 --> 01:12:09,506
I know. That made me emotional.

1250
01:12:12,276 --> 01:12:14,145
Gosh, I feel bad.

1251
01:12:14,146 --> 01:12:15,185
I know.

1252
01:12:15,186 --> 01:12:17,416
(Other parents feel bad as well.)

1253
01:12:22,356 --> 01:12:23,726
She has grown a lot.

1254
01:12:25,596 --> 01:12:26,955
Why am I in tears when she isn't my daughter?

1255
01:12:26,956 --> 01:12:29,466
- I know.
- It's heartbreaking.

1256
01:12:29,726 --> 01:12:30,766
My heart aches.

1257
01:12:42,076 --> 01:12:46,246
Still, I had a fun time while being on the show.

1258
01:12:49,986 --> 01:12:51,186
I like your phone case.

1259
01:12:53,086 --> 01:12:58,256
(Shall we switch our phone cases during the date?)

1260
01:12:58,456 --> 01:13:00,456
- Come on.
- Oh, no!

1261
01:13:02,426 --> 01:13:04,095
I think it's late,

1262
01:13:04,096 --> 01:13:08,706
but I think I still plucked up my courage.

1263
01:13:08,736 --> 01:13:11,136
And I said everything I wanted.

1264
01:13:11,306 --> 01:13:14,035
I think I got to learn...

1265
01:13:14,036 --> 01:13:16,806
a lot about myself.

1266
01:13:17,306 --> 01:13:18,445
I have no regrets.

1267
01:13:18,446 --> 01:13:20,445
(I have no regrets.)

1268
01:13:20,446 --> 01:13:22,645
Right. Seo Yoon did a great job.

1269
01:13:22,646 --> 01:13:23,915
(Seo Yoon did her best and left no regrets.)

1270
01:13:23,916 --> 01:13:25,356
Without regrets.

1271
01:13:26,056 --> 01:13:27,215
Because she's my child.

1272
01:13:27,216 --> 01:13:28,586
- Right.
- Exactly.

1273
01:13:28,786 --> 01:13:32,856
I appeared on TV for a long time since I played sports.

1274
01:13:33,426 --> 01:13:35,495
But I don't think I've cried like this before on TV.

1275
01:13:35,496 --> 01:13:38,696
- Right.
- I never really had a reason to.

1276
01:13:39,096 --> 01:13:41,336
My kid makes me cry.

1277
01:13:42,066 --> 01:13:44,836
My kid actually hesitated so much about doing this.

1278
01:13:45,376 --> 01:13:47,636
Although she hesitated, I think it was a good idea.

1279
01:13:48,046 --> 01:13:51,476
I have two daughters.

1280
01:13:53,176 --> 01:13:54,916
After I got divorced,

1281
01:13:55,046 --> 01:13:58,355
their value became even bigger.

1282
01:13:58,356 --> 01:13:59,356
I see.

1283
01:13:59,357 --> 01:14:00,856
At the end,

1284
01:14:01,156 --> 01:14:04,825
when she said I'd be sad...

1285
01:14:04,826 --> 01:14:06,295
- We were overwhelmed by that too.
- Exactly.

1286
01:14:06,296 --> 01:14:08,695
I believe that is...

1287
01:14:08,696 --> 01:14:11,126
our priceless...

1288
01:14:12,536 --> 01:14:14,766
communion and rhythm.

1289
01:14:15,406 --> 01:14:17,806
I'm actually very grateful for her,

1290
